         Mobs do summon pets. Just is not seen much because they dont normally get aggro especially on raids or groups. Go solo Fallen Soldiers in the up, pull with slow, add your dots and fd and you will see your pet get summoned over and over again. I have noticed the spec pet with the latest changes does seem to gain aggro much more often, and even seems to tank mobs fairly decent now if it has to be done.</P><P>Cyph</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Cyphler on 09/14/2002  14:47:26<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
